# 🍔 FoodieExpress – Online Food Delivery Website

A responsive, interactive food delivery website built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. Users can browse a visually rich food menu, view items dynamically, and manage a simple shopping cart experience — all in a single-page design.

---

## 💻 Tech Stack

- **Frontend**: HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript
- **Tools**: VS Code, Git, GitHub
- **Fonts**: Google Fonts – Poppins

---

## 🌟 Features

- 🖼️ Hero section with background image and branding
- 🧾 Interactive food menu with images and prices
- 🛒 Add-to-Cart buttons for each food item
- 🧺 Dynamic cart area that updates in real time
- 📱 Fully responsive layout for all screen sizes
- 📞 Contact section with email, phone, and address
- 🔗 Clean navigation and semantic HTML structure

